# Substack publication URL (no trailing slash).
# Get this by creating a publication at https://substack.com — the subdomain
# you pick becomes <name>.substack.com, and the RSS feed lives at /feed.
# Example:
#   SUBSTACK_URL=https://yourname.substack.com
# When unset, the blog falls back to local markdown files in /posts.
SUBSTACK_URL=
